# =========================================================
# üß† Full-Stack Project .gitignore (React + Node + Express + MongoDB + pnpm + TypeScript + Mongoose + Tailwind CSS)
# =========================================================
# üìå Description:
# This .gitignore file is crafted for a **modern full-stack TypeScript project**.
# It supports both frontend (React + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS) and backend
# (Node.js + Express + MongoDB + Mongoose) environments ‚Äî using **pnpm** as the package manager.
#
# ‚ö†Ô∏è IMPORTANT:
# This file is specifically for **TypeScript-based projects**.
# Do NOT use it in pure JavaScript projects, 
# (Because it ignores compiled `.js` and `.d.ts` files  #  generated from `.ts` source files)
#
# üßæ Purpose:
# - Prevent sensitive data (.env files) from being committed.
# - Ignore build outputs, caches, dependencies, logs, and editor configs.
# - Keep your Git repository clean, lightweight, and secure.
#
# Author: Yash Mishra
# GitHub: https://github.com/YashMishra0101/fullstack-ignore-templates
# =========================================================


